. edit examples/fs.conf for your system
. edit examples/server.conf for your system

. create a trove space using one of the following methods:
  - running the pvfs2-server with the -f option
  - running test/io/trove/trove-mkfs

. the pvfs2-server program takes two arguments:
  - a path to the fs.conf file
  - a path to the server.conf file

. start running tests from the test/server directory
